Subdivision AA—Application of the Regulatory Powers Act—
Infringement notices
100  Infringement notices
Provisions subject to an infringement notice
(1) The following provisions are subject to an infringement notice 
under Part 5 of the Regulatory Powers Act:
(a) the provisions of Division 3 (civil penalties);
(b) subsection 115D(1) (vacancy fee liability—vacancy fee 
return);
(ba) subsection 115DA(1) (vacancy fee liability—false or 
misleading vacancy fee return);
(c) subsection 115G(1) (vacancy fee liability—requirement to 
keep records);
(d) section 130ZV (civil penalty for failing to give notice to 
Registrar).

